  "narrative_arc": "Lithuanian immigrant whose entire family is destroyed by the meatpacking industry. Sinclair documents every system failure: the scam home purchase, the injury with no workers comp, the wife's sexual assault by a foreman, the child's drowning in an unpaved street, the jail for punching the foreman. Layer by layer, every system extracts from him until nothing remains.",
  "why_this_character_matters": "Jurgis is the most complete fictional dome in American literature. Sinclair fills every layer with documented industrial-era conditions. Building his dome with 1906 vs. 2024 systems reveals exactly which protections were added and which gaps remain.",
